WEBVTT

00:01.769 --> 00:03.671
[Tasha] Previously on Power...

00:03.703 --> 00:05.172
Where's Dad?

00:05.206 --> 00:07.074
You the man of the house,
a'ight?

00:07.108 --> 00:08.109
Hold it down.

00:08.141 --> 00:09.610
-A'ight.
-I love you.

00:09.643 --> 00:11.078
Nothing's the same
with him anymore.

00:11.112 --> 00:13.447
Everything's just different.
He's different.

00:13.481 --> 00:15.216
[Raina]
I'm worried about you, 'Riq.

00:15.249 --> 00:16.650
There was this cop at school
looking for you today.

00:16.684 --> 00:18.552
Are you in trouble?
You should tell Mom.

00:18.586 --> 00:20.187
Listen to me.
You cannot tell anyone.

00:20.221 --> 00:21.789
-You can't.
-I won't tell.

00:22.022 --> 00:23.124
I swear.

00:23.157 --> 00:24.592
I know who you are, Ray Ray.

00:24.625 --> 00:27.328
You need to leave
my brother alone.

00:27.361 --> 00:28.796
[gunshot]

00:29.029 --> 00:31.065
[dramatic music plays]

00:31.098 --> 00:32.500
[Tariq]
Raina was my better half.

00:32.533 --> 00:36.103
When I-when I find myself
in a place of trouble,

00:36.137 --> 00:37.705
I think to myself...

00:37.738 --> 00:39.373
"What would Raina do?"

00:39.407 --> 00:40.775
[Tasha] Well, here we are.
This is Choate.

00:40.808 --> 00:42.076
There's something
I gotta say to you.

00:42.109 --> 00:43.411
You deserve the truth.

00:43.444 --> 00:45.212
We thought we were
protecting you,

00:45.246 --> 00:47.448
but all we did
was teach you how to lie.

00:47.481 --> 00:50.684
I told her I-I would handle it,
but I watched her die.

00:50.718 --> 00:52.653
-[Tariq] I miss her so much.
-[Tasha] I miss her too.

00:52.686 --> 00:53.788
[Effie] What happened
to your sister?

00:53.821 --> 00:54.789
You were twins?

00:54.822 --> 00:57.091
Yeah, and half of me is gone.

00:57.124 --> 00:58.592
-I feel so alone.
-You're not alone.

00:58.626 --> 01:00.094
I'm here.

01:00.127 --> 01:02.296
♪ ♪

01:02.329 --> 01:04.331
[Orson] He's expelled,
effective immediately.

01:04.364 --> 01:05.800
[Tariq] That's all it is.
It's just baby aspirin.

01:05.833 --> 01:08.569
[Orson] Do they think
they're buying baby aspirin?

01:08.602 --> 01:09.770
[Tariq] Ma, what happened
to your arm?

01:09.804 --> 01:11.071
[Tasha] Ghost happened
to my arm.

01:11.105 --> 01:12.306
He laid hands on me.

01:12.339 --> 01:14.508
And I would kill Ghost
to protect you, 'Riq.

01:14.542 --> 01:16.110
I should be the one
protecting you!

01:16.143 --> 01:17.278
And I will.

01:17.311 --> 01:18.579
I promise you that, Ma,
no matter what.

01:18.612 --> 01:20.314
-A'ight.
-[Tariq] Don't get it twisted.

01:20.347 --> 01:22.349
You might've given me life.

01:22.383 --> 01:23.818
But you were never
my fucking father.

01:23.851 --> 01:25.486
He said he would kill you?

01:25.519 --> 01:26.854
He didn't have to say it, Ma.

01:27.087 --> 01:28.122
I'm gonna stop him.

01:28.155 --> 01:29.590
If you don't want this,

01:29.623 --> 01:31.525
'Riq, you gotta tell me now.

01:31.559 --> 01:33.227
Ma, I just don't want you
to go to jail.

01:34.328 --> 01:35.329
I won't.

01:35.362 --> 01:37.264
[Kanan]
What if she gets caught?

01:37.298 --> 01:39.200
[Tariq] Man, she ain't gonna
get caught; she too smart.

01:39.233 --> 01:40.601
There's only one way
to be sure.

01:40.634 --> 01:41.869
It was always
gonna go this way.

01:42.102 --> 01:43.404
Just gotta step into it.

01:43.437 --> 01:45.739
[Ghost]
Tariq, if you do this shit,

01:45.773 --> 01:47.641
you can never go back.

01:47.675 --> 01:50.678
I'd do anything to go back...

01:50.711 --> 01:54.148
to go back to how it was
before you left us for Angela.

01:54.181 --> 01:56.851
[tense music plays]

01:56.884 --> 01:58.786
[gunshot]

01:58.819 --> 02:00.688
-Come on!
-Wait.

02:00.721 --> 02:02.223
We take care
of each other, right?

02:02.256 --> 02:03.757
Right.

02:03.791 --> 02:07.428
♪ ♪

02:07.461 --> 02:09.697
-[Tariq] I saw you at Truth.
-Wasn't me.

02:09.729 --> 02:10.798
I don't want to have to say
I saw you

02:10.830 --> 02:12.233
if you're not the one
that did it.

02:12.266 --> 02:14.468
-Dre did it, right?
-Right, it was Coleman.

02:14.502 --> 02:15.636
Good.

02:15.669 --> 02:18.205
The entire portfolio
goes to your children.

02:18.239 --> 02:20.174
