-[Tasha] What do you want now?

02:35.422 --> 02:37.358
Tasha Green St. Patrick,
you're under arrest

02:37.391 --> 02:38.492
for the murder
of James St. Patrick.

02:38.526 --> 02:39.593
No, she didn't do it.

02:39.627 --> 02:40.694
Mom, tell her
you didn't do this!

02:40.728 --> 02:41.729
Tell her what really happened!

02:41.762 --> 02:43.397
Tariq, go to school!

02:43.430 --> 02:44.632
No.

02:44.665 --> 02:47.301
Live your life.

