05:01.001 --> 05:03.604
[Meredith]
First-degree murder.

05:03.637 --> 05:06.440
You don't look like
you could pull that off.

05:06.473 --> 05:08.375
Nails too nice for that.

05:09.977 --> 05:11.545
My husband beat me up, a'ight?

05:11.578 --> 05:13.614
[scoffs]
You're not a battered woman.

05:13.647 --> 05:16.417
I've seen a million girls
with that same story

05:16.450 --> 05:18.052
here and at Bedford Hills.

05:18.085 --> 05:20.587
If they didn't find you
crying on the ground

05:20.621 --> 05:23.090
next to the body,
that's bullshit.

05:23.957 --> 05:26.694
Maybe you could sell
that shit to the jury

05:26.727 --> 05:28.562
but not to me.

05:28.595 --> 05:30.597
[gate buzzes]

05:30.631 --> 05:31.965
She's headed to arraignment.

05:31.999 --> 05:34.902
Good luck,
Tasha Green St. Patrick.

05:34.935 --> 05:36.437
If the locals don't keep you,

05:36.470 --> 05:39.073
I'll see
your guilty ass tonight.

05:39.106 --> 05:41.108
[Meredith laughs]

05:41.341 --> 05:43.544
[gate slams]

05:43.577 --> 05:46.680
♪ They made a monster
Out of me ♪

05:50.117 --> 05:52.986
Listen, you need to come
and stay with me right now.

05:53.020 --> 05:54.955
Grandma, I have to stay
at Stansfield.

05:54.988 --> 05:56.557
It's what Ma wants.

05:56.590 --> 05:59.426
No, your mother doesn't know
what's best for you right now.

05:59.460 --> 06:02.062
She has enough to worry about.

06:02.096 --> 06:03.931
'Riq, please come home
with us.

06:03.964 --> 06:06.567
I mean, I would think
that you would want family

06:06.600 --> 06:07.768
at a time like this.

06:07.801 --> 06:09.737
You don't understand, Grandma.
I do, but--

06:09.770 --> 06:11.105
[Tameika]
Mrs. Green.

06:11.138 --> 06:13.006
I'm Tameika Washington,
Tasha's attorney.

06:13.040 --> 06:14.775
-Nice to meet you.
-You too.

06:14.808 --> 06:16.477
[Tameika]
This must be Yasmine.

06:16.510 --> 06:18.746
-And you're Tariq.
-Yeah, so what happens today?

06:18.779 --> 06:20.380
Does she get bail?
I brought money.

06:20.414 --> 06:21.949
One step at a time, Tariq.

06:22.983 --> 06:24.918
We're gonna argue
a justification defense.

06:24.952 --> 06:26.587
That means Tasha
says she did it.

06:26.620 --> 06:28.655
What?
No!

06:28.689 --> 06:30.691
She has to say
she killed James

06:30.724 --> 06:32.426
but she did it
in self-defense.

06:32.459 --> 06:34.628
It's her best chance
at less jail time

06:34.661 --> 06:35.896
or maybe none at all.

06:35.929 --> 06:37.798
Wait, so she has to say
she did it in court?

06:37.831 --> 06:39.566
Yes, and your mother
is very sure

06:39.600 --> 06:41.168
that's what she wants to do.

06:41.401 --> 06:43.670
Wait, no, I-I need
to speak to her first.

06:43.704 --> 06:44.938
Her mind's made up.

06:44.972 --> 06:48.008
Tariq, in order to get
the judge to give bail,

06:48.041 --> 06:50.911
I need to say some pretty ugly
things about your father.

06:50.944 --> 06:52.813
Are you gonna be okay
with that?

06:53.680 --> 06:54.948
Go ahead.

06:56.049 --> 06:57.084
Okay.

06:57.117 --> 07:00.087
[gentle music plays]

07:00.120 --> 07:02.022
♪ ♪

07:02.055 --> 07:04.558
Tasha St. Patrick had a plan,
and she executed it.

07:04.591 --> 07:06.193
She duped her lover,
Quinton Wallace,

07:06.426 --> 07:08.162
into driving her
to the scene of the crime.

07:08.195 --> 07:09.830
She waited until her husband

07:09.863 --> 07:11.632
turned off all the cameras
at Truth,

07:11.665 --> 07:13.433
and she calmly
pulled the trigger,

07:13.467 --> 07:16.036
with her unwitting
getaway driver waiting outside.

07:16.069 --> 07:17.805
She showed premeditation
with malice aforethought.

07:17.838 --> 07:19.006
She even had a scapegoat

07:19.039 --> 07:20.874
all lined up
in case she got caught.

07:20.908 --> 07:22.042
She committed
first-degree murder,

07:22.075 --> 07:23.577
and she deserves no bail.

07:23.610 --> 07:25.078
She thought he was gonna
kill her, Your Honor.

07:25.112 --> 07:26.847
Can the defense prove
that James St. Patrick

07:26.880 --> 07:27.948
made such a threat?

07:27.981 --> 07:29.550
We can show the bruises
on her arm

07:29.583 --> 07:31.585
from the conversation they had
about it the night before.

07:31.618 --> 07:33.854
Your Honor,
Ms. Washington can't argue

07:33.887 --> 07:36.523
that the defendant thought
she was in imminent danger

07:36.557 --> 07:37.991
-24 hours later.
-She's right, Ms. Washington.

07:38.025 --> 07:40.928
Your Honor,
James St. Patrick was a monster

07:40.961 --> 07:42.696
of untold proportion.

07:42.729 --> 07:45.465
The Democratic candidate
for lieutenant governor

07:45.499 --> 07:46.700
was a monster?

07:46.733 --> 07:47.968
The Democrats
didn't do their homework

07:48.001 --> 07:49.469
on James St. Patrick.

07:49.503 --> 07:52.506
He was suspected of
and investigated for

07:52.539 --> 07:55.475
multiple homicides,
numerous narcotics charges,

07:55.509 --> 07:58.245
and violations of laws
both state and federal.

07:58.478 --> 08:00.214
James St. Patrick was cleared
of the only charge

08:00.247 --> 08:01.582
ever brought against him.

08:01.615 --> 08:03.116
[Tameika] Your Honor,
if we go to trial,

08:03.150 --> 08:04.484
I will show that my client

08:04.518 --> 08:06.220
was the long-suffering wife

08:06.253 --> 08:08.121
of a smiling sociopath,

08:08.155 --> 08:11.024
a man as vicious
as he was successful,

08:11.058 --> 08:14.528
as capable of slitting a throat
as he was of making a speech.

08:14.561 --> 08:16.697
My client is not
a flight risk.

08:16.730 --> 08:18.265
She has children.

08:19.233 --> 08:21.268
I ask you, Your Honor,

08:21.501 --> 08:23.570
what kind of a stand
against battered women

08:23.604 --> 08:24.805
would you like to make?

08:24.838 --> 08:26.106
Hmm.

08:27.241 --> 08:29.910
Ms. Sullivan, it sounds like
you need to call your boss

08:29.943 --> 08:31.712
before you go too far
with this prosecution.

08:31.745 --> 08:32.980
Thank you, Your Honor.

08:33.013 --> 08:34.780
[Galanti]
Oh, don't thank me yet.

08:34.815 --> 08:36.817
Your client is facing
murder one.

08:36.850 --> 08:38.784
I can't just let her go home.

08:38.818 --> 08:42.823
Tasha Green St. Patrick,
you are remanded to custody.

08:42.856 --> 08:45.092
-No bail.
-[gavel bangs]

08:45.125 --> 08:47.828
No bail! [sobs]

08:47.861 --> 08:49.596
Is Mommy coming home?

08:51.598 --> 08:53.133
Not yet, Yas.

08:53.166 --> 08:54.601
[dramatic music plays]

08:54.635 --> 08:56.069
[Jenny]
This is Jenny Sullivan.

08:56.103 --> 08:58.038
-I need to speak to...
-[cell phone buzzes]

08:58.071 --> 08:59.973
♪ ♪

09:00.007 --> 09:01.975
Take her to the attorney
conference room.

09:02.009 --> 09:03.577
I think we have a meeting.

09:03.610 --> 09:06.613
♪ ♪

09:10.317 --> 09:12.586
How was your phone call
with the DA?

09:12.619 --> 09:13.754
I'm here, aren't I?

09:13.787 --> 09:15.689
We want
criminally negligent homicide,

09:15.722 --> 09:16.924
E felony, probation.

09:16.957 --> 09:18.025
She showed up with a gun,

09:18.058 --> 09:19.226
and she pulled the trigger,
Tameika.

09:19.259 --> 09:21.094
What the hell is negligent
about that?

09:21.128 --> 09:24.031
Man two,
I'll recommend five years.

09:29.102 --> 09:30.570
[tense music plays]

09:30.604 --> 09:31.772
[Jenny]
He killed all those people?

09:31.805 --> 09:33.640
[Tameika] And more
we couldn't nail him for.

09:33.674 --> 09:35.242
Hell, we couldn't nail him
for these; he was that good.

09:35.275 --> 09:38.312
My client knew she'd be just
another one of these photos,

09:38.345 --> 09:40.213
either herself
or her children.

09:40.247 --> 09:42.082
[Jenny] You didn't prove any
of this; it's not admissible.

09:42.115 --> 09:43.684
[Tameika] My client's
state of mind is at issue,

09:43.717 --> 09:45.919
not the evidence.

09:45.953 --> 09:48.121
Tasha, do you think James
committed these murders?

09:48.155 --> 09:51.158
♪ ♪

09:52.926 --> 09:55.162
I know I would have been next.

09:55.195 --> 09:57.164
[Tameika] I put these photos in
front of a jury, it's a walk.

09:57.197 --> 09:59.232
Shit, they'd throw her
a goddamn parade.

09:59.266 --> 10:01.101
You might not get them in--
fair warning.

10:01.134 --> 10:02.636
[Tameika] But I sure will try,

10:02.669 --> 10:05.005
and once the entire
Democratic Party is humiliated,

10:05.038 --> 10:06.740
let's see where you end up--

10:06.773 --> 10:08.742
fair warning.

10:08.775 --> 10:11.778
♪ ♪

10:12.713 --> 10:15.716
